	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" >I would LOVE to have 2h be a viable way of dishing out damage.  At the very least I would like the high end 2h weapons do much greater damage than dual wielding.<br>
<br>
Dual wield = greater taunt<br>
2h = More damage<br>
<br>
